      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>永久設立之大型防禦性軍事據點，經特別強固，部份會包含城鎮。較「堡壘（forts）」更大及堅固。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
